descriptionNullable:
### Content

The information about the folder contents are as follows:
1. Blood : Faces containing blood
2. NoBlood : Faces not containing blood
3. Faces: Contains cropped images of faces
The aim is to build a model that will be able to detect and differentiate a face with blood and the one without.


### Acknowledgements

This dataset is the courtesy of [Tessact](http://tessact.com/)

subtitle: Image Classification
